window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>He's protecting his former flame... but can he resist falling for her?</b></p> <p>Lana is about to begin the most important trial of her career: prosecuting a murderer who's long evaded justice. But her sexy star witness keeps catching her eye. Even worse? They share a history. Years ago, they spent three incredible nights that she still can't get out of her head.</p> <p>Max Bennett hasn't been able to forget about Lana, either. But he has a rule: no more than three nights with any womanâ€”ever. This soldier-turned-executive has always made a better problem solver than a boyfriend.</p> <p>When a faceless stalker threatens Lana, Max will go to any lengths to protect her. The real challenge? Trying not to fall for her.</p> <p>This second-chance romance features steamy flashbacks, courtroom drama, and heart-pounding danger! Each book in the Bennett Security series can be enjoyed as a standalone.</p>"; 
